 //// import React from 'react' ;  //import  is a ES6 feature

it means ->hm React class import kar rhe ha react folder se

// import './index.css';  // kue yeh file isliyee hamne from use nhi  kea haa
css ki file bhi hmm import karne ki liye react me method use karte ha


// export default App;
it means : hm sirf aik class export kar rhe haa
agar hamne aik se zeada component ka store karwana ho tuu hmm 
default nhi laghee gee
Then we use this syntax
export{
  component 1,
  component2, comp3 .....
}
on the other hand in APP.js we import using this syntax{ .. , ..}
