------------------------------BOOTSTRAP------
https://react-bootstrap.github.io/getting-started/introduction

for installing bootsrap

npm install react-bootstrap bootstrap

for connecting css
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';// in index.js


For using MATERIAL UI
https://mui.com/getting-started/installation/

for installing
npm install @mui/material @emotion/react @emotion/styled

agar hamne aik se zeada component ka store karwana ho tuu hmm 
default nhi laghee gee
Then we use this syntax
export{
  component 1,
  component2, comp3 .....
}

html to jsx convert compiler use for convert html to jsx
https://magic.reactjs.net/htmltojsx.htm
